Title: 'Our roots: hardships then and now'
DateModified: '2018-01-21'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/our-roots-hardships-then-and-now
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Savana Burdick-Perez
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: I travel to the places in Argentina that my father and aunt fled during the
  Dirty War and compare it to the struggles he faced moving here. I relay what the
  country is like now, socially and politically, and I reconnect with the relatives
  I have left there.
